<p style="margin: 12px 0px 12px 0;">A career within Bank of America's Global Consumer &amp; Small Business Banking group is your opportunity to:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Attract, develop, and strengthen relationships with consumer and small business customers worldwide</li>
	<li>Leverage the power of our global resources and products to deliver solutions that meet the unique needs of customers</li>
